column7: Vector of codes associated with the question
column8: Dates when this question was attempted
column9: Total attempts; Attempts without help; Attempts with help
column10: Days Since Last Attempt: The number of days that have passed since your most recent attempt on the question, irrespective of the method used.
column11: Longest Memory Interval: The maximum number of days between any memory-based attempt and the attempt immediately preceding it (regardless of whether that preceding attempt was solved from memory or with help)
column12: Latest Memory Interval: The number of days between your most recent memory-based attempt and the previous attempt, calculated only if your latest attempt was solved from memory.
column13: Potential Memory Gains in days: The estimated improvement in your Latest Memory Interval, expressed in days, if you successfully answer the question from memory today.
column14: Potential Memory Gain as a multiplier of my LaMI: Proportional increase in your Latest Memory Interval if you answer the question from memory today.
column15: 0 = I did the question with help \n 1 = I did the question from memory only
